channel.title: I can't run my 508? [BULBY]
channel.description:
When I run my 508, I get this error: java.net.BindException: Address already in use: JVM_Bind at java.net.PlainSocketImpl.socketBind(Native Method) at java.net.PlainSocketImpl.bind(Unknown Source) at java.net.ServerSocket.bind(Unknown Source) at java.net.ServerSocket.<init>(Unknown Source) at java.net.ServerSocket.<init>(Unknown Source) at Bulby.net.SocketListener.<init>(SocketListener.java:36) at Bulby.Server.main(Server.java:57) Press any key to continue . . .
Any help on that?
